.. activecode:: ER1006
    :author: Eric Reed
    :difficulty: 3
    :basecourse: fopp
    :topic: Sequences/Exercises
    :from_source: F


    Write code that asks the user for a word, and reports
    whether it is a palindrome.
    bob is a palindrome because it reads the same forwards
    and back.  brenda is not.
    ~~~~